{"type":"text","timestamp":1783410450437,"sessionID":"ses_0c4747a96ffep3NBgTFCEHGj4H","part":{"id":"prt_f3b8bdbff001HCESWxQrjBb0CG","messageID":"msg_f3b8bcc3b001w02ZFA5sM4YIzR","sessionID":"ses_0c4747a96ffep3NBgTFCEHGj4H","type":"text","text":"```json\n{\n  \"anomaly_ids\": [],\n  \"answer\": \"根据《XX证券授权管理办法》附件二《费用报销审批权限表》，单笔费用报销金额达到10,000元（含）以上、50,000元（不含）以下的，必要审批角色为部门总经理。因此，单笔报销达到10,000元（壹万元）即需要部门总经理审批。\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"03_authorization_management.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"附件二 (AR-03)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```","time":{"start":1783410449407,"end":1783410450407}}}
